Description: SkillFishOS BC-250 kernel (linux-tkg 7.0.11-skillfishos)
 Meta-package that fetches and installs the prebuilt linux-tkg 7.0.11-skillfishos kernel
 (image + headers) for the AMD BC-250 from the SkillFishOS GitHub release. The
 ~150 MB kernel image is a release asset because GitHub's 100 MB/file limit
 prevents shipping it in the APT pool. The download + install runs out-of-band
 (after the apt transaction releases its lock).

